txt.en: Natsulm the Night-raider can be found in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should defeat Natsulm the Night-raider.
The fearsome warg called Natsulm the Night-raider stalks those who venture too far into the Wildwood.
Natsulm the Night-raider can be found in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should find Natsulm the Night-raider.
The fearsome warg called Natsulm the Night-raider stalks those who venture too far into the Wildwood. Defeating this fearsome beast will assist in returning safety to the Wildwood.
